List out what you&#8217;re thankful for and tell your followers to comment with theirs</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>T</strong>houghtful friends <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f46f-200d-2642-fe0f.png" alt="üëØ‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></li>
